OL,6,FJoan Mcalpine, Project Director of The
OL,7,FRobert Burns Ellisland Trust, says
OL,8,Fmuch of the facility is not fit for
OL,9,Fpurpose.
OL,11,FShe said: "These old buildings are in
OL,12,Fa very serious state of deterioration
OL,13,Fand they've had inappropriate repairs
OL,14,Fin the past, which have led to
OL,15,Fdampness in the walls, many of them
OL,16,Fjust aren't fit for purpose.
OL,18,F"The full cost of restoring Ellisland
OL,19,Fis about #7.4m to make it an
OL,20,Finternational visitor centre.
