OL,6,FThe historic buildings, including the
OL,7,FScottish Bard's cottage, were taken
OL,8,Fover by The Robert Burns Ellisland
OL,9,FTrust in 2020. They aimed to create
OL,10,Fsustainable income which would allow
OL,11,Fthe facility to continue welcoming
OL,12,Fvisitors from all over the world.
OL,14,FThe trust hopes to raise more than #7m
OL,15,Fto help finance an immersive visitor
OL,16,Fexperience and a gallery.
OL,18,FEleanor Kane, a musician, says the
OL,19,Fmoney will help bring the farm to "its
OL,20,Ffull potential".
